<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.1.2">
<l>kavaḷamā katatta kariyuyyap poykaik karāmkoḷak kalaṅkiyuḷ niṉaintu</l>
<l>tuvaḷamēl vantu tōṉṟivaṉ mutalai tuṇipaṭac cuṭupaṭai turantōṉ</l>
<l>kuvaḷainīḷ muḷari kumutamoṇ kaḻunīr koymmalar neytaloṇ kaḻaṉi</l>
<l>tivaḷumā ḷikaicūḻ ceḻumaṇip puricait tirukkaṇṇaṅ kuṭiyuṇiṉ ṟāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When a crocodile in a pond caught a great maddened elephant with musth,</l>
<l rend="indent">as it bowed, weeping, reflecting in its heart,</l>
<l>The one who, appearing coming from above hurled his fiery weapon</l>
<l rend="indent">so that the strong crocodile was cut to pieces</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] so that [the elephant] escaped,</l>
<l>Stands in Tirukkaṇṇaṅkuṭi with thick, beautiful walls encircled by mansions</l>
<l>Where glitter bright paddy fields with dark lilies, tall lotuses, white waterlilies,</l>
<l rend="indent">bright red lilies, [and] waterlilies with pluckable blossoms.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
